nodes.text: Green Dystopia was one of the barrooms of Quarek'k, a large bar complex located on Coruscant shortly after the rise of the Galactic Empire.

In 19 BBY, the bounty hunter Aurra Sing visited the bar during her hunt for the former Jedi Jax Pavan. Sing was told to seek out Calathi, who was in the Green Dystopia, by the Crimson Redrum bartender when Sing asked for information regarding Pavan.
